data.description: JUST REDUCED 10K!! Seller offers $4500 towards closing costs at list price! Spacious home in a secure gated community on a large corner lot! This light filled home has 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and a huge 3 car garage! Living area has vaulted ceilings, a cozy fireplace, and opens to the large kitchen with an island, a large pantry, and a butlers pantry! One bedroom with a full bath downstairs and three additional bedrooms upstairs with a huge primary bedroom and a balcony that gives you stunning mountain views! Primary bedroom has his and hers walk-in closets, a large bathroom with double sinks, walk-in shower, and a nice garden tub. A huge xeriscaped backyard perfect for your summer BBQ! Quick access to I-25,  stores, restaurants, & parks.  Priced to sell.
